message.body: i@x@ @Yup yup. I'll call tomorrow. For now, back to school for project. And, business expansion plan. Bubble tea, bagels, and pizza all in one magical place. B
i@x@ !@ecause though this is good pizza, $9.15 for 2 slices aint right ha
Haha. I wouldn't know. I guess if anything is above a buck a slice I ain't having it! Haha jk. I'm still gonna eat it.
Wait a second!!! You got bubble tea?
Ha maybe 2 bucks...to be fair. But thats quite enough
No haha. I got pizza!
But they sell bubble tea?
Haha no no no. I just want to bring the proper versions of pizza, bagels, and bubble tea to DC at not awful prices!
OHHHHH! Hahaha. I get ya now.
...that'd be...interesting.
It would be the most popular place in the city...CLEARly.
Like a sam's, tea do, and Lorenzo's pizza all mashed together? Oh hot damn, let's add some macaroons!
Aaaand gelato? And what the heck is lorenzo's??! Try brother brunos, or tonys touch, or neils if your desperate. Lorenzos?? Nah.
...why would I want my pizza from Tony's touch? Ha weirdo! Haha.
Its tonys touch of italy!!
More like Tony's touch of contamination! I kid. I've never had pizza from them. Pizza from Chuck-e-cheese is good.
Ew no groooooss, baby. This is gourmet! No chuck. Never chuck.
Hahaha. Chuck is delicious!
Hes not an authentic italian.
He's not a real person.
Wull thur ya go
Haha "thur."
Sorry, baby! I'll call ya in a little.
....I'm on campus. I made the trek. I have decided to seclude myself in a cubicle on the 2nd or 3rd floor where I will essentially do nothing but chemistry until my lab period.
This is either a fabulous idea or a major downfall.
Hahaha. I've been sitting in this cubicle for the past 5 hours. My stomach keeps growling. Boo.
Haha darling lovely, go eat!! No more cubicle. That sounds yicky
I've actually been pretty productive. It's nice. But my stomach is betraying me on the 3rd floor.
Haha you gonna get a bite?
I have a pretzel with me :)
Haha ok. That counts a lil bit
Yes. Until dinner time.
Haha terrible baby. You need to feed yourself ya know
I know. But I'm like you. I'm sick of food. No more until I see you!!
Ahah oh goodness! We gonna be sticks!
No. I won't. You might. I'll still eat. DUN YOU WORRY!
Haha ok. As long as you promise.
I do I do.
